Nc6 $17 {Jimenez Martinez,J (2243)-Sivuk,V (2523)/La Roda op 46th 2019 (4)/0-1}
) ({A game between two giants of the past went} 9. Ned2 c5 $1 10. a3 Bxd2+ 11.
Qxd2 O-O 12. dxc5 Rd8 13. Qc2 Na6 {, and Black was fine. It is very
instructive to see how a nice position evolved into a huge advantage from here:
} 14. Be2 Nxc5 15. O-O Bd7 16. Rac1 Ba4 $1 17. Qc3 Qxc3 18. Rxc3 Bb3 $1 $19 {
[%csl Gd1][%cal Yd8d1] ;Smyslov, V (2560)-Gligoric,S (2560)/EU-Cup 02nd
quarterfinal 1979 (3.2)/0-1, with positional domination by Black.}) 9... Qf4 $1
{The most principled reaction.} ({The calmer} 9... Qd8 {gives White enough
time to solve the king's issues, but it worked nicely after careless play by
White in the following game:} 10. g3 O-O 11. Bg2 Be7 12. Qc2 $2 (12. Re1 $142 {
[%cal Ge2f1] was necessary.}) 12... Nd7 13. Rhd1 Qc7 14. Rac1 f5 $1 15. Nc3 e5
