[%csl Re2][%cal Ge5e4,Gf5f4] ;Peters,J (1761)-Hauch,J (2126)/Bad Zwesten op
4th 2000 (3)/ 0-1, with a strong attack.}) (11. Ng3 $2 {is even worse. How can
