Qxf3 Qxf3 21. gxf3 exd4 22. exd4 Nb6 $5 ({Black is also fine after} 22... Rd8
23. Rd1 Ne5 24. Be2 Ng6 $11 {[%cal Gg6f4]}) 23. Nxb6 Rxb6 $11 {Kramnik,V (2772)
-Leko,P (2738)/Miskolc m rapid 2007 (7)/1/2-1/2, and White is unable to
