Gg4] simply looks pleasant for Black.}) 15... Bf5 $1 {[%cal Ge5e4]} 16. Nd2 Bd4
17. Nde4 Qd8 $15 {[%cal Yf5g6,Gf7f5] , and I like Black's chances: the bishops
