17. Bxf3 Bd4 $11) 17. Nd1 $2 ({White misses the tactical idea} 17. Nxe5 $1 Bxe2
18. Nxe2 Qxe5 19. Qxc5 $14) 17... Bxf3 18. Bxf3 {Black had a solid position,
and from now he started to play for more:} Bd4 {[%csl Gd4]} 19. Nc3 a4 $1 20.
Ne2 c5 21. Rfd1 a3 $1 22. b3 Bb2 23. Rb1 c4 $17 {Potkin,V (2557)-Kobalia,M  
