9... cxd4 10. exd4 Nd7 ({Black is also fine after} 10... Nc6 11. Nxc6 bxc6 12.
Bxc4 Be7 13. O-O O-O 14. Rfd1 a5 $11 {[%cal Gc8a6,Yf8d8,Ya8b8]}) 11. Nxc4 (11.
