1. d4 d5 2. c4 c6 3. Nc3 Nf6 4. Nf3 e6 5. Bg5 h6 6. Bxf6 Qxf6 7. e3 {Let's
study the main path now.} g6 $5 {I like this move-order, as Black keeps some
