The bishop has nothing to do on g4 now.} 16. Rad1 Rac8 17. dxc6 (17. Qb1 c5 $1
18. Nd2 c4 19. Bc2 Bf8 $1 $15 {[%cal Gg7f8,Gf8c5] looks already pleasant for
Black. Bf8-c5 is another typical manoeuvre, which shows that the dark-squared
