now.} 16. dxc5 Qxc5 17. O-O Qd6 18. Rfd1 Ra3 19. Qb2 O-O $11 {[%cal Yc8e6] ,
and Black is OK.}) 15... Be6 16. Qb3 Nd7 {Yu,Y (2750)-Giri,A (2769)/Shenzhen
Du Te Cup 2017 (4)/ 1/2-1/2 And Black is fine. The c6-pawn can be well
defended, and he had no problems developing, with an equal game.} *

