{Black has an important idea to try to reduce the potential of White's
initiative in the centre here. What is it?} 11... Nh5 $1 {[%csl Gg3][%cal
Gd4d5] This bishop would be very dangerous if the centre became open.
Therefore, Black rushes to get rid of it.} ({On the other hand, after} 11...
Qb6 12. Ne5 Bg7 13. h4 $1 $36 {, White keeps some pressure.}) 12. d5 $1 cxd5
13. exd5 exd5 14. Nxd5 Nxg3 15. hxg3 Bg7 $13 {With a double-edged position and
chances for both sides.} *

