{Black's position may seem a bit weird, but not to Shirov. Try to find the way
he solved Black's problems here.} 21... Ne5 $1 {A nice tactical resource.} 22.
g4 (22. Rxd8+ Qxd8 23. Qxe5 Qd1+ 24. Qe1 Qd3+ 25. Qe2 Qxf5 $19) 22... f6 23. g3
